</div>
<div>
<p>王棠<pc>，</pc>
<placeName>涿州</placeName>新城人<pc>。</pc>博古善屬文<pc>。</pc>重熙<measure quantity="15" unit="years">
<num value="15">十五</num>年</measure>擢進士<pc>。</pc>鄉貢<pc>、</pc>禮部<pc>、</pc>廷試對皆第<num value="1">一</num>
<pc>。</pc>累遷上京<term>鹽鐵使</term>
<pc>。</pc>或誣以賄<pc>，</pc>無狀<pc>，</pc>釋之<pc>。</pc>遷東京戶部使<pc>。</pc>大康<measure quantity="2" unit="years">
<num value="2">二</num>年</measure>
